action.description: From printer. To engrossment. Engrossed. First reprint.Read third time. Amended. (Amend. No. 16.)Dispensed with reprinting.Read third time. Passed, as amended. Title approved. (Yeas: 22, Nays: 20.)To printer.From printer. To reengrossment. Reengrossed. Second reprint.To Senate.In Senate.Read first time. Referred to Committee on Jobs and Economy. To committee.From committee: Do pass.
